missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: Imperial intelligence got wind of the political shift on Sullust and moved quickly to lock it down. Their chief political official has been arrested and is being transported to an imperial prison. This is our opportunity to secure Sullustan support for the Alliance. Gold Squadron will jump in and destroy the shuttles escort. While Y-Wings from Red Squadron jump in to disable the prison shuttle. Before our Rescue transport jumps in to liberate their leader.
Red Squadron head to the jump point immediately. Gold Squadron is already en route.
Gold Squadron target those Tie Fighters. Red Squadron switch to ion cannons and disable those Sentinels. I'll take the Lambda.
Those fighters are all cleared okay, you sure you want us to jump home?
Thanks Gold Squadron, we'll manage from here.
Right Red Leader. Gold Squadron on me.
Target ship disabled. Activating beacon for boarding craft.
Hostage secured. Commence release from docking.
Another Lancer class frigate is entering the area. Prepare for more fighters!
Thanks for the cover Gold squadron. We'll see you back at the fleet.
Okay Red Squadron. Drop your targets and make a break for the jump point.
This is Rescue One, the target is marked and we're beginning our approach.
